{"tid":21073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條新聞好多疑點","createTime":"2016-12-03T15:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T04:24:45.000Z","uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa8305f2f937507f404ed305eda3f08cf1fbf78","tid":21073,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161203/55998824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161203%2F55998824&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7608ae4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161203%2F55998824&h=6906ae6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161203/55998824</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【私人恩怨】南加州大學華裔教授被捅死 男學生被捕<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【更新內容】<br />\n<br />\n美國南加州大學一名華裔男教授，在校園遭人捅死，被捕疑犯是一名男學生，初步估計是因個人恩怨而起。中新社引述當地傳媒報道指，遇害的教授在讀書時曾擔任學校的香港同學會主席，有可能是生於香港。<br />\n事發在當地周五中午，25歲心理學教授曾曉峰（Bosco Siaufung Tjan）在自己的實驗室被刺，當場喪命。曾曉峰2001年起在大學教書，2015年正式成為大學的終身教授，他亦專責大腦和認知科學方面研究，也是大學認知神經影像中心主任。<br />\n警方未有交代疑犯姓名，校園一度向師生發短訊，促他們遠離科學及醫科課室所在的教學大樓，但同時強調校園其他地方仍然安全。<br />\n南加州大學並非首次捲入血案，2014年中國留學生紀欣然在校園附近遭多名劫匪毆打致死；2012年中國留學生瞿銘及吳穎，將寶馬停泊在校園附近談心，結果雙雙遭劫匪轟斃。<br />\n美聯社/中新社"},{"pid":"fd7423a223b871b410f7947b5c29a4eb7dbf1ff9","tid":21073,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"104dc46a194f8568f89bb52cbc240474a99b31b2","tid":21073,"uid":44476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:02:08.000Z","msg":"25歲做教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2001年姐係10歲開始教書??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83b752f3f96c02e35ea7a446476380b7f7ad019","tid":21073,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"25歲心理學教授曾曉峰（Bosco Siaufung Tjan）在自己的實驗室被刺，當場喪命。曾曉峰2001年起在大學教書，2015年正式成為大學的終身教授"},{"pid":"7bdd32687260445bf8c56ac846c2ca48c670090f","tid":21073,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1348cbbbfae5963455ea70c423da65493330e86b","tid":21073,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"「遇害的教授在讀書時曾擔任學校的香港同學會主席，有可能是生於香港。」但個英文譯名唔似香港人"},{"pid":"864c030283893b4b488097e7a1a1418b79a40ad0","tid":21073,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「遇害的教授在讀書時曾擔任學校的香港同學會主席，有可能是生於香港。」但個英文譯名唔似香港人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n似台灣人"},{"pid":"55d2a600c03741bdcdedf3d54173dd1987382180","tid":21073,"uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"全美第二多中國人大學<br />\n入唔到ucla 比多啲錢就入到usc"},{"pid":"c4609b36f1d35e3ee9e1792af46f9bd2083c23ee","tid":21073,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"咁有咩疑點？<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\nlink都唔識貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eb6717f45c4634a60bed75983129c4d025bd03","tid":21073,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"疑點係邊？小弟不才體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b96b6e3bcc0927d8e021c44b4d9518145d3c28","tid":21073,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"個疑點咪係25歲終身教授點樣由2001起喺間大學到教書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff8d9a191ea2472431b6e9232bc0e1f901937eb","tid":21073,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>疑點係邊？小弟不才體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用下個腦"},{"